# FinZ Backend API — Walkthrough

Backend REST API untuk **FinZ — AI-Powered Personal Financial Advisor** telah selesai dibangun dan divalidasi. Semua endpoint berjalan penuh dengan data nyata dari MySQL.

---

## Struktur Project

```
finz-backend/
├── .env                        ← Konfigurasi environment
├── package.json
└── src/
    ├── app.js                  ← Express setup, CORS, middleware, routing
    ├── server.js               ← Entry point, DB connect → listen
    ├── config/
    │   └── database.js         ← Sequelize + MySQL config
    ├── models/
    │   └── Transaction.js      ← Sequelize model (tabel transactions)
    ├── controllers/
    │   ├── transactionController.js
    │   ├── dashboardController.js
    │   └── aiController.js
    ├── services/
    │   ├── transactionService.js  ← CRUD business logic
    │   ├── dashboardService.js    ← Agregasi & perhitungan bulan ini
    │   └── aiService.js           ← Mock AI: prediksi, klasifikasi, score
    ├── routes/
    │   ├── transactionRoutes.js
    │   ├── dashboardRoutes.js
    │   └── aiRoutes.js
    ├── middlewares/
    │   ├── validators.js       ← express-validator rules
    │   ├── requestLogger.js    ← Colorized request log
    │   └── errorHandler.js     ← Global error handler
    └── database/
        └── seeder.js           ← 30 transaksi dummy realistic
```

---

## Cara Menjalankan

```bash
# 1. Install dependencies
npm install

# 2. Buat database MySQL (Laragon sudah aktif)
# Database: finz_db sudah dibuat

# 3. Isi data dummy (30 transaksi)
npm run seed

# 4. Jalankan server development
npm run dev
# → http://localhost:8000
```

