## Semua Endpoint API

### Transactions CRUD

| Method | Endpoint | Keterangan |
|--------|----------|------------|
| `GET` | `/api/transactions` | List semua (+ filter `?category=&date_from=&date_to=`) |
| `GET` | `/api/transactions/:id` | Detail satu transaksi |
| `POST` | `/api/transactions` | Buat transaksi baru |
| `PUT` | `/api/transactions/:id` | Update transaksi |
| `DELETE` | `/api/transactions/:id` | Hapus transaksi |

### Dashboard

| Method | Endpoint | Keterangan |
|--------|----------|------------|
| `GET` | `/api/dashboard` | Summary bulan ini (`?user_id=1`) |

### AI Mock Services

| Method | Endpoint | Keterangan |
|--------|----------|------------|
| `POST` | `/api/predict/balance` | Prediksi saldo akhir bulan |
| `POST` | `/api/predict/category` | Klasifikasi kategori dari deskripsi |
| `GET` | `/api/recommendation/:user_id` | Rekomendasi finansial |
| `GET` | `/api/financial-score/:user_id` | Health score keuangan |

